Package: libdsc0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libc6 (>= 2.14)
Suggests: libdsc-doc
Description: High-performance data structures library for C (runtime)
 libdsc is a comprehensive collection of generic data structures implemented
 in C11, designed for high performance and ease of use. It provides:
  * Vector - Dynamic array implementation
  * List - Doubly linked list
  * Queue - FIFO data structure
  * Stack - LIFO data structure
  * Map - Hash table implementation
  * Set - Unique element container
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

