Depends: libdsc0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         pkg-config,
         gcc (>= 8) | clang (>= 7)
Suggests: libdsc-doc
Description: Development files for libdsc (generic)
 libdsc is a comprehensive collection of generic data structures implemented
 in C11, designed for high performance and ease of use. It provides various
 data structure implementations including vectors, lists, queues, stacks,
 maps, and sets.
 .
 This package contains the development files including:
  * Header files
  * Static library
  * CMake configuration files
  * API documentation

